      "content": "**MEMORANDUM: KYC COMPLIANCE FRAMEWORK FOR NEW FINTECH CLIENT**\n\n**1. OBJECTIVE AND SCOPE**\nThis document outlines the mandatory **regulatory compliance** protocols designed to effectively combat **financial crime**, **money laundering**, and **terrorist financing** within our new fintech client's operations. The core strategy relies on a strict **risk-based approach** to ensure **customer due diligence** is executed rigorously for all accounts.\n\n**2. ONBOARDING AND IDENTITY VERIFICATION**\nUpon initiation, we must perform **identity verification** and **verification of identity** using secure **procurement of documents**. This process includes **sanctions screening** and **PEP screening** to identify **politically exposed persons**. We will conduct **checking against lists** to filter out any **adverse media** or high-risk entities. The **ultimate beneficial owner** and **beneficial ownership** structures must be fully disclosed to satisfy **anti-money laundering** requirements.\n\n**3. SOURCE OF FUNDS AND WEALTH**\nClients are required to provide detailed **source of funds** and **source of wealth** declarations. This is critical for **enhanced due diligence** when dealing with clients",
